      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against canonical benchmark problems including lid-driven cavity and Taylor-Couette flow. Published verification studies confirm second-order spatial accuracy of the pressure-velocity coupling scheme used. No additional code verification was performed by the project team, consistent with MRL 2 reliance on vendor-supplied verification evidence."
