      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions are fully documented in Hariharan et al. (2011) and Herbertson et al. (2013). Inlet flow rates, rotational speeds, fluid properties (bovine blood analogue), and temperature are specified. CFD boundary conditions were set to match reported experimental values within measurement uncertainty. Test condition correspondence is well-established for this widely-used benchmark dataset."
    },
