      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted RH index within 20% of experimental values across all five validation operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RH index compared against experimental measurements at all five flow-speed combinations. Maximum relative error 13.4% at the 2 L/min, 3500 RPM operating point. All other points within 10%. The 20% acceptance threshold is met at all operating points. Agreement is sufficient to support use of the model for comparative worst-case identification under MRL 2."
