      "rationale": "Validation was performed using the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same geometry used in the COU. Operating conditions in validation (2–8 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) fully encompass the COU operating range. Fluid properties in validation experiments match those assumed in COU simulations. The validation-to-COU relevance is strong, with geometry, operating conditions, and fluid properties all matched."
    },
    {
